Approach 1 (Brute Force)

class Solution {
    public int addDigits(int n) {
        while(n > 9) {
            int sum = 0;
            while(n > 0) {
                sum += n % 10;
                n = n / 10;
            }
            n = sum;
        }

        return n;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(log n)
Space Complexity : O(1)

Approach 2 (Optimized)

class Solution {
    public int addDigits(int n) {
        if(n == 0) return 0;
        else if(n % 9 == 0) return 9;
        else return n % 9;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O()
Space Complexity : O()
